          "lang_word": "optional",
          "definition": "adj. 可選擇的、非強制的、選購的"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "Attendance at the training session is optional but highly recommended.",
          "highlight": [
            "optional"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "培訓課程的出席是可選擇的，但強烈建議參加。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The extended warranty is more optional on budget models than on premium ones.",
          "highlight": [
            "more optional"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "延長保固對入門款機型而言，比對高階款更屬於可有可無的選項。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Of all the add-ons, the engraving service is the most optional for most customers.",
          "highlight": [
            "most optional"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "在所有加購項目中，雕刻服務對大多數顧客來說是最可有可無的。"
          }
        }
