          "lang": "zh-TW",
          "lang_word": "paycheck",
          "definition": "n. 薪水、薪資支票"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "Employees receive their paycheck on the last business day of each month.",
          "highlight": [
            "paycheck"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "員工在每個月的最後一個工作日領到薪水。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Many workers live from paycheck to paycheck without any savings.",
          "highlight": [
            "paycheck"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "許多勞工靠著每個月的薪水勉強度日，毫無積蓄。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Missing two paychecks in a row would be disastrous for the family.",
          "highlight": [
            "paychecks"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "連續少領兩份薪水對這個家庭來說將是場災難。"
          }
        }
      ],
      "synonyms": [
        "salary",
        "wages",
